headline: Cartera Celebrates 20 Years of Loyalty Innovation and Leadership
summary: Cartera, the loyalty commerce platform trusted by many of the world's leading airlines, banks, and retailers, proudly celebrates its 20th anniversary this year. Founded in Lexington, Mass., in 2005, Cartera has grown from a local startup to a behind-the-scenes industry leader, driving over $14 billion in sales for its partners and delivering 3 billion points and miles to loyalty program members each year.
